    "description": "The Tottori Bank, Ltd. provides various banking products and services in Japan. The company offers deposit products; housing, renovation, car, education, card, travel, and other loans; and internet banking services. It also provides individual defined contribution pension, individual annuity and variable, term, whole life, medical, cancer, income protection, and student endowment insurance products. In addition, the company offers management support services, such as consulting, business matching, expansion support, medical and nursing care business support, business M&A, entrepreneurship start-up support, business insurance, and decarbonized management services; and fundraising, account transfer and other services. Further, it provides freee, a cloud accounting software; payment solution; forex trading services; kintone, a business improvement platform; Office, a platform that supports information sharing and communication; Smaregi, a POS system; and KING OF TIME, an attendance management system. The company was incorporated in 1921 and is headquartered in Tottori, Japan."
